17 Commissioner of the MA Department of Environmental Protection or a designee, and 5 members
18 drawn from a range of energy advocacy NGOs including The Conservation Law Foundation,
19 Eco-Nuclear Solutions, and other such organizations designated by each of the two co-chairs of
